abstract: >
  Interactive web tool for exploring the Layton/Hu human nephron mathematical
  model. Built with Streamlit, DuckDB and Plotly. Provides multi-scenario
  comparison (baseline, sex differences, diabetes, hypertension, SGLT2
  inhibition), automatic mass/volume interpretation of concentration changes,
  and an educational layer with citation-attributed content.
